OL,3,CD-Day 80 The Last Veterans: Jack
OL,4,CMortimer
OL,6,FJack Mortimer, Age 100, Royal Army
OL,7,FOrdnance Corps
OL,9,FInterviewed 11 October 2023
OL,11,FIn a jeep driving onto Sword Beach on
OL,12,FD-Day, Jack Mortimer was a driver and
OL,13,Fdispatch rider with the 12th Ordnance
OL,14,FBeach Detachment.
OL,16,FBeach Groups organised the flow of
OL,17,Ftroops following the landings,
OL,18,Fincluding controlling the movement of
OL,19,Fvehicles to inland assembly points.
