OL,3,CD-Day 80 The Last Veterans: Jack
OL,4,CMortimer
OL,6,FHe said: "There were about 60 storemen
OL,7,Fif you like. Storemen of a different
OL,8,Fclass. Soldiers that knew all
OL,9,Fammunition, how to store it.
OL,11,F"And petrol of course. All this is
OL,12,Fnecessary behind the fighting soldier.
OL,14,F"In the 6th Beach Group were
OL,15,Fdetachments of all corps. Trained to
OL,16,Fland. We trained with Naval commandos."
OL,18,FHe remembers his landing very clearly.
