OL,3,CD-Day 80 The Last Veterans: Jack
OL,4,CMortimer
OL,6,F"There was a trailer behind me full of
OL,7,Fammunition - and my motorbike. My
OL,8,Fmotorbike, smashing bike.
OL,10,F"I was more or less the last one to
OL,11,Fjoin on the ferry so I was the first
OL,12,Foff. There was a big lift and it went
OL,13,Fdown and I have told many many people
OL,14,Fabout how we got off. I was sat there
OL,15,Fin the jeep and the door opened and
OL,16,Fthere was a big what we call an
OL,17,Falligator - a big raft. And the two
OL,18,Framps - and the sea wasn't all that
OL,19,Fcalm.
