OL,3,CD-Day 80 The Last Veterans: Jack
OL,4,CMortimer
OL,6,F"There was a sailor there with a red
OL,7,Flight and a green light and it was
OL,8,F'When the green light is on, get
OL,9,Fyourself off.'
OL,11,F"And I was looking down at the sea and
OL,12,Fthen it was bang on. That was it. I
OL,13,Fnever got my feet wet."
OL,15,FMr Mortimer's section created
OL,16,Fammunition and petrol dumps. He later
OL,17,Fjoined the fighting in Caen.
