OL,3,CD-Day 80 The Last Veterans: Jack
OL,4,CMortimer
OL,6,FHe said: "I am proud to be a D-Day
OL,7,Fveteran. I don't brag about it. I was
OL,8,Fonly one of 130,000 soldiers, sailors
OL,9,Fand airmen.
OL,11,F"We were all trained to do a little
OL,12,Fjob. And we all did it well.
OL,14,F"And all those little bits came
OL,15,Ftogether to make a gigantic effort
OL,16,Fthat rid Europe of the Nazi tyranny."
